---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 315
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=The Manifold Content of Symbols
By: Ibn 'Arabi
---
All these figures of speech should be regarded as symbols of sublime
mysteries and Divine illuminations vouchsafed to me by the Lord God.
Turn thy thoughts, oh! reader, from the mere words and seek the hidden
meaning that thou mayest understand.
